15	//
16	//     MATCH        a door asserts a value and it agrees with the verified expectation
17	//     ABSTAIN      a door omits or marks needs-review a value the set expects       (allowed, logged)
18	//     OK*          a door's expectations are met by abstention because the CAPTURED bundle is an
19	//                  explicit unreachable (bot-walled / SPA shell)                     (allowed, logged)
20	//     MISSING      no fixture on disk for a verified firm - an uncovered gap         (FAIL, exit 2)
21	//     CONTRADICT   a door asserts a value that disagrees with a verified expectation (FAIL, exit 1)
