76	// The single resolved-address guard, built once from the real resolver. Passed as the request
77	// `lookup` option (below) so every DNS answer - initial hop AND every redirect hop - is validated
78	// against the private/loopback/link-local blocklist before a socket is opened. The hostname string
79	// is checked by parseSafeFetchTarget; the resolved IP is checked here; one door decides both.
